"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-comment-olympics-paris-2024-simone-biles-imane-khelif-adam-peaty-andy-murray-b1174979.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Comment  Get our award-winning daily news email featuring exclusive stories, opinion and expert analysis    I would like to be emailed about offers, event and updates from Evening Standard.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourprivacy notice.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Who could have watched theOlympicsover the past two weeks and not looked within oneself and found oneself wanting?\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been awe-struck by the competitors.\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 602, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Impressed beyond belief by their skill, dedication, and how much they must have sacrificed to get there.\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 707, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And scared for them too, because their drive will have caused them harm, and some of the sacrifices they have made may not have been worth it.\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not crying because I have come second, I am crying because it took so much to get here,\\\" saidAdam Peaty, Britain's star breast-stroke swimmer, whomissed out on gold in the men's 100m breaststrokeby a heartbreaking two hundredths of a second.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6654948171555344, \"rank\": 0.5026412988148469, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty, who has spoken openly about his battles with mental health said, \\\"I am an older man here now.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not have that relentless pursuit every single day without a sacrifice of some sort.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That sacrifice can come in many ways.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can come in time, it can come in energy, it can come in relationships.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes in every single form.\\\"\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1435, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Who did not brush away a tear watching the great Andy Murray exit elite sport's beautiful, savage stage?\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1486, \"end\": 1497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2781297928547762e-44, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Invented by the ancient Greeks in 776\\u2009BC when they were held as part of a religious festival at Olympia, the games have no doubt stood the test of time because they show our beautiful, majestic, flawed human condition in all its glory and frailties.\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1561, \"end\": 1575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999993152303048, \"rank\": 5.667728496182898e-07, \"text\": \"ancient Greeks\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Greece\"}, {\"begin\": 1583, \"end\": 1585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 0.999999878117713, \"rank\": 9.167030471693226e-08, \"text\": \"BC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}, {\"begin\": 1641, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4445110917424264e-14, \"text\": \"Olympia\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Excellence, determination, hunger for victory, loss and triumph.\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of human life is here, and all of its complications, as we saw withthe awful showdown in the boxing matchbetween Angela Carini andImane Khelif, who has been banned from competing in women's titles by the International Boxing Association.\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 2102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1978, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 2069, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.686469990255749e-21, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a highly charged scene at the North Paris Arena where Carini was struck by multiple powerful blows, she surrendered after just 46 seconds and fell to her knees sobbing.\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2142, \"end\": 2147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.511299470046869e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piero_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9760276891015702, \"rank\": 0.024561097155633066, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piero_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piero_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not fair,\\\" she said, \\\"It's not fair.\\\"\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Has life been fair for Khelif either; is it ever?\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2368, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Scenes of amazing human drama like this have united us all at a time of national friction as we gather around televisions and cheer on athletes who we have often never heard of.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2547, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And those of whom over the years we have become familiar with, and fond.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Who would not cheer for star gymnastSimone Biles, who, after a troubled last Olympics in Tokyo has, on what she describes as her \\\"redemption tour\\\", won a stunning three gold medals in Paris; as she teaches us that it's possible to dazzle sometimes, and sometimes you fail, too.\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2712, \"end\": 2717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9992467691389494, \"rank\": 0.0007537984699074109, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2807, \"end\": 2812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.511299470046869e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024 LIVE!\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sky Brown in action; Team GB miss out on equestrian medal; Josh Kerr later; Day 11 latest  Paris Olympics 2024: Adam Peaty cries 'happy tears' despite missing out on 100m breaststroke gold  Simone Biles: how she became the greatest gymnast of all time  Olympics 2024: Andy Murray 'genuinely happy' after bidding farewell to tennis on own terms  Or the pathos of watching Brit heroAndy Murray's glittering careerdraw to a close on Thursdayas he and Dan Evans were knocked out in the Olympic men's doubles quarter-finals.\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 3441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2943, \"end\": 2950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999999959073, \"rank\": 4.256699691733501e-12, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2963, \"end\": 2973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9999422229755119, \"rank\": 5.777397937010539e-05, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}, {\"begin\": 3013, \"end\": 3027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3034, \"end\": 3044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 3370, \"end\": 3379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"score\": 0.6049885640602598, \"rank\": 0.6529238061766037, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Who did not brush away a tear to watch the two-time Olympic champion, three-time Grand Slam champion, former world No\\u20091 and arguably Britain's greatest ever athlete exit elite sport's beautiful, savage stage?\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3575, \"end\": 3582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.6654948171555344, \"rank\": 0.5026412988148469, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Dreams do come true, if only we wish hard enough.\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can have anything in life if you will sacrifice everything else for it,\\\" said JM Barrie.\", \"from\": 3703, \"to\": 3795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3785, \"end\": 3794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._M._Barrie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JM Barrie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._M._Barrie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._M._Barrie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, that's what the Olympics celebrates.\", \"from\": 3797, \"to\": 3841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision to dedicate everything in your entire life to that one three-minute swimming race.\", \"from\": 3842, \"to\": 3937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And although it's not a choice most of us would make, and not one I would do myself or recommend to my children, you have to applaud the romanticism of it.\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 4093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of us understand the equation and decide to go in a different direction.\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What an incredible privilege it is to watch these superhumans in Paris who choose instead to try, and risk it all.\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4238, \"end\": 4243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.511299470046869e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anna van Praagh is the Evening Standard's chief content officer  MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope 